cURL Example:
curl -X POST 'https://<controller>/proxy/network/v2/api/site/{site}/app-traffic-rate?start=1756219634886&end=1756306034886&includeUnidentified=true' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{
  "client_macs": [
    "c4:38:75:ee:45:e2"
  ]
}'

